{"tid":2247281,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做左兩個月廣東話Podcast  你問我答","createTime":"2020-10-17T17:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T14:01:10.000Z","uid":288072,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad858819cde8e1217018a7b49a1cc489549e96ca","tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"8月尾開始做，而家差唔多做左2個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩出果陣上過香港Podcast排行榜第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家總排行榜第二十位，商業排行榜第一位。<br />\n<br />\n如果對做Podcast有任何問題既都可以問我。因為我都好新，未必樣樣識，答到你既一定盡答。<br />\n係聽眾既話唔介意你問私人野/無聊野 (當然自爆野唔答)，財經野唔答啦平時答到好攰<br />\n<br />\n深夜無聊吹下水，因為feel到今日會好夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果冇人問就會自己沉 因為我p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMy channel: <a href=\"https://invest.soci.vip/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvest.soci.vip%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=2943acef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://invest.soci.vip/</a>      (如果對投資有興趣既就Follow啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"fd96eb4e837c798c5f47205ac8852e4bcc98ef42","tid":2247281,"uid":320861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"4000個view啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有fol你ig"},{"pid":"470af22e65e8e3bfa071f65b9c72165fc04a6df9","tid":2247281,"uid":355887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"你個名咩意思"},{"pid":"1d940fa305a659de6f716d22ccd69681610790ac","tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd96eb4e837c798c5f47205ac8852e4bcc98ef42","tid":2247281,"uid":320861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:02:14.000Z","msg"