"tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470af22e65e8e3bfa071f65b9c72165fc04a6df9","tid":2247281,"uid":355887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"你個名咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"你指連登名定channel名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"both la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"連登ACC 係借人地  因為我原本acc太多膠post<br />\n所以個名唔關我事<br />\n我資深連登仔  從來都冇p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學已經上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChannel名係覺得平時網上d投資教學太多廢話<br />\n哂大家時間(time cost 都係錢)，10分鐘講完既野可能花成個鐘講，之後講唔夠幾句又叫你買course<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最大問題係班友自己都唔知係咪有trade/有穩定profit<br />\n想斷班&quot;名師&quot;財路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢邊免費既埋黎睇埋黎簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4945b3d3c35575ad3ea8ae43158a5942faa4109","tid":2247281,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"有聽開你"},{"pid":"4b249f9904bc09a8b15113f352a1e19d4f9b8ddd","tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f4945b3d3c35575ad3ea8ae43158a5942faa4109","tid":2247281,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"有聽開你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"多謝支持!<br />\n<br />\nIn case有人唔知，不如我講下Podcast係d咩。<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講就係聲音版既Youtube。好似電台咁你自己錄完一集之後將佢upload上去apple podcast/spotify/kkbox 等等既平台<br />\n<br />\n咁聽眾就可以禁入去你頻道簡佢地想聽既集數"},{"pid":"09f809c52d74961b7df100427cd955da47d235e6","tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"再簡單講下Podcast有咩好處/壞處:<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n1. 暫時仲有100%言論自由，你鍾意講粗口講色情野講政治野完全冇人會理你/審查你既內容。<br />\n2. 唔需要d咩技術，youtube都要識剪片，podcast你就咁用手機錄都得<br />\n3. 香港暫時仲係一個藍海，聽眾少，podcaster更加少。暫時唔會點樣同人撞內容。<br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n1. 0收入，純粹義工，唔會好似youtube咁有分紅。<br />\n2. 香港聽眾少，太冷門既野可能冇人聽<br />\n3. 聽眾少+冇收入好容易會令你放棄，同埋完全0機構支援，咩都係靠自己。台灣同外國好hit，有好多機構會搞活動/幫podcaster宣傳"},{"pid":"4a80a8ceb6c9e07bf5f75904e0ba03a6dc165154","tid":2247281,"uid":238868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"其實係IG push 你俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.住外國揸車聽 podcast 多，而家疫情關係揸少咗車你個 show 三十分鐘啱啱好，台灣果面 podcast 業爆得好勁製作好好但係超多業配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋 1.4x 1.5x 倍速聽唔明....<br />\n<br />\n想問下你用咩 equipment 錄 podcast , setup 係點? 後製又要搞幾耐..?"},{"pid":"5fcf98a03146f085e52e3b6ce651997a28f7071e","tid":2247281,"uid":288072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a80a8ceb6c9e07bf5f75904e0ba03a6dc165154","tid":2247281,"uid":238868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"其實係IG push 你俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.住外國揸車聽 podcast 多，而家疫情關係揸少咗車你個 show 三十分鐘啱啱好，台灣果面 podcast 業爆得好勁製作好好但係超多業配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋 1.4x 1.5x 倍速聽唔明....<br />\n<br />\n想問下你用咩 equipment 錄 podcast , setup 係點? 後製又要搞幾耐..?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"多謝支持~<br />\n我都想學佢地後製  不過自己懶<br />\n同埋覺得我講既內容都唔需要點後製<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係獨白<br />\n<br />\n我錄音用RODE NT-USB Mini (市價大約9xx)，因為一開始已經諗住長錄<br />\n錄音software用audacity(免費)，後製都係用audacity<br />\n<br />\nsetup係冇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲d有收入唔排除會upgrade<br />\n而家係自己房錄，因為我做trade有3個mon，我會將3個mon拍埋做正方形，支咪擺中間當做左少少隔音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (心諗jm9)<br />\n<br />\n我一集平均十分鐘， 打稿+錄+後製 大約搞半日到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" 